cent to a target, an Avka Young deals +2d6 damage to that target with a successful attack.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Avka Young","cl":6,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":9,"senses":"Perception\u00a0+2","perception":2,"reflexDefense":18,"flatFootedDefense":17,"fortitudeDefense":13,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":53,"damageThreshold":18,"speed":"4 Squares (Walking), 6 Squares (Flying); Hunger-Driven Frenzy","melee":"Claws (2) +7 (1d4+2)","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":5,"grapple":7,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":14,"dexterity":12,"constitution":15,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":13,"charisma":6},"feats":["f8e2a30390d870e7","96666de28ba99b64","11db29efd899c438"],"skills":["Initiative\u00a0+9 (may reroll, must take second result)"],"abilityText":"Hunger-Driven Frenzy:\u00a0Whenever an Avka Young hits the same target with two Claw attacks during a\u00a0Full Attack\u00a0Action, the Avka Young can move three squares. This movement does not provoke\u00a0Attacks of Opportunity.\nSwarm Attack:\u00a0When at least one other Avka Young is adjacent to a target, an Avka Young deals +2d6 damage to that target with a successful attack."}}},"items":[]}
{"_id":"0609a158ad64175f","name":"Dinko Pack","type":"npc","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"isDroid":false,"droidDegree":"","attributes":{"str":{"base":2,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"dex":{"base":18,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"con":{"base":10,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"int":{"base":1,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"wis":{"base":12,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"cha":{"base":8,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0}},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"climb":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"deception":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"endurance":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"con","favorite":false},"gatherInformation":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"initiative":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"jump":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"knowledgeBureaucracy":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeGalacticLore":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeLifeSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgePhysicalSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeSocialSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTactics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTechnology":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"mechanics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"perception":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"persuasion":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"pilot":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"ride":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"stealth":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"survival":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"swim":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"treatInjury":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"useComputer":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"useTheForce":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false}},"hp":{"value":28,"max":28,"temp":0,"bonus":0},"conditionTrack":{"current":0,"persistent":false,"penalty":0},"level":4,"size":"medium","speed":6,"defenses":{"reflex":{"total":19,"armor":0,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"dex","source":"level","level":0},"fort":{"total":10,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"con","level":0},"will":{"total":11,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"wis","level":0},"flatFooted":{"total":15}},"languages":[],"destinyPoints":{"value":0,"max":0},"forcePoints":{"value":0,"max":0,"die":"1d6"},"darkSideScore":0,"damageThreshold":20,"bab":1,"race":"","class":"","className":"","biography":"Motion Vision:\u00a0The eyes of a Dinko have evolved such that they see only movement. The creature takes a -5 penalty to attack rolls against opponents that have not moved in the previous round. Although a Dinko cannot see its opponent, its keen sense of smell alerts it to the presence of potential prey (See Scent).\nPoison:\u00a0If the Bite attack of a Dinko deals damage to a living target, the target is also poisoned. If the poison succeeds on an attack roll (1d20+8) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense, the target moves -1 step along the\u00a0Condition Track.\nA target moved to the end of the\u00a0Condition Track\u00a0by the poison is\u00a0Immobilized, but not unconscious. The Poison attacks each round until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.\nScent:\u00a0Dinkos ignore\u00a0Concealment\u00a0and\u00a0Cover\u00a0when making\u00a0Perception\u00a0checks to\u00a0Notice\u00a0opponents within 10 squares, and they take no penalty from poor visibility when\u00a0Tracking.\nStench:\u00a0Dinkos exude a foul stench that nauseates most other creatures. If the Stench succeeds on an attack roll (1d20+5) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense, the target becomes nauseated for 1 round. A nauseated target can make only a single\u00a0Move Action\u00a0that round. The Stench attacks each round that the target remains within 2 squares of the Dinko.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Dinko Pack","cl":4,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":10,"senses":"Motion Vision, Scent,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+7","perception":7,"reflexDefense":19,"flatFootedDefense":15,"fortitudeDefense":10,"willDefense":11,"hitPoints":28,"damageThreshold":20,"speed":"6 Squares","melee":"Bite -3 (1,\u00a0Area Attack) plus Poison","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":1,"grapple":-10,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":2,"dexterity":18,"constitution":10,"intelligence":1,"wisdom":12,"charisma":8},"feats":["a9f6de36f24ef202","252b67d6e31c377e"],"skills":["Initiative\u00a0+10,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+7"],"abilityText":"Motion Vision:\u00a0The eyes of a Dinko have evolved such that they see only movement. The creature takes a -5 penalty to attack rolls against opponents that have not moved in the previous round. Although a Dinko cannot see its opponent, its keen sense of smell alerts it to the presence of potential prey (See Scent).\nPoison:\u00a0If the Bite attack of a Dinko deals damage to a living target, the target is also poisoned. If the poison succeeds on an attack roll (1d20+8) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense, the target moves -1 step along the\u00a0Condition Track.\nA target moved to the end of the\u00a0Condition Track\u00a0by the poison is\u00a0Immobilized, but not unconscious. The Poison attacks each round until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.\nScent:\u00a0Dinkos ignore\u00a0Concealment\u00a0and\u00a0Cover\u00a0when making\u00a0Perception\u00a0checks to\u00a0Notice\u00a0opponents within 10 squares, and they take no penalty from poor visibility when\u00a0Tracking.\nStench:\u00a0Dinkos exude a foul stench that nauseates most other creatures. If the Stench succeeds on an attack roll (1d20+5) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense, the target becomes nauseated for 1 round. A nauseated target can make only a single\u00a0Move Action\u00a0that round. The Stench attacks each round that the target remains within 2 squares of the Dinko."}}},"items":[]}
