a0Vacuum\u00a0of space and can maneuver without any hindrance or penalty in\u00a0Vacuum.\n00:00\n41:20","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Mynock Swarm","cl":3,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":6,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+8","perception":8,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFootedDefense":10,"fortitudeDefense":15,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":42,"damageThreshold":25,"speed":"10 Squares (Flying (Vacuum\u00a0Only));\u00a0Running Attack","melee":"Wing Buffet (2) +0 (1d4,\u00a0Area Attack)","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":1,"grapple":6,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":8,"dexterity":20,"constitution":20,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":14,"charisma":10},"feats":["4d6a68d553fb0449"],"skills":["Perception\u00a0+8"],"abilityText":"Space-Dwelling:\u00a0Mynocks are silicon-based life forms that take no damage from exposure to\u00a0Vacuum. However, they take the same damage from being in a planetary atmosphere that ordinary life forms take from being in a\u00a0Vacuum.\nFly Through Space:\u00a0Mynocks can fly in the\u00a0Vacuum\u00a0of space and can maneuver without any hindrance or penalty in\u00a0Vacuum.\n00:00\n41:20"}}},"items":[]}
