onus on melee attack rolls and melee damage rolls until the end of its turn.\nShadow Cloak:\u00a0As a\u00a0Standard Action, a Devourer can surround itself with dark shadows, gaining\u00a0Total Concealment\u00a0from all targets until it makes an attack or until the end of its turn, whichever comes first.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Devourer","cl":6,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":4,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+5","perception":5,"reflexDefense":17,"flatFootedDefense":16,"fortitudeDefense":15,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":67,"damageThreshold":20,"speed":"8 Squares;\u00a0Powerful Charge","melee":"Bite +12 (1d8+10); Claws (2) +12 (1d6+10); Gore +12* (1d8+17) with\u00a0Powerful Charge","fightingSpace":"2x2 Squares","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":5,"grapple":17,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":25,"dexterity":12,"constitution":21,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":14,"charisma":13},"feats":["3f76464c43c73f84","e73873cdc77a6451","1592aaedf4b6e40a"],"skills":["Stealth\u00a0+9"],"abilityText":"Dark Saturation:\u00a0Once per encounter as a\u00a0Free Action, a Devourer can infect a target that it has just damaged with\u00a0The Dark Side. Treat this as\u00a0Sith Poison.\nMutant Rage:\u00a0Once per encounter as a\u00a0Swift Action, a Devourer can enter a Mutant Rage, gaining a +4 Rage bonus on melee attack rolls and melee damage rolls until the end of its turn.\nShadow Cloak:\u00a0As a\u00a0Standard Action, a Devourer can surround itself with dark shadows, gaining\u00a0Total Concealment\u00a0from all targets until it makes an attack or until the end of its turn, whichever comes first."}}},"items":[]}
