ortitude Defense. On a hit, the target takes 3d6 points of damage and moves -1 step along the\u00a0Condition Track. The Poison attacks each round at the start of the Battle Hydra's turn until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Battle Hydra","cl":8,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":15,"senses":"Low-Light Vision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+9","perception":9,"reflexDefense":30,"flatFootedDefense":23,"fortitudeDefense":22,"willDefense":19,"hitPoints":67,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"6 Squares (Walking), 10 Squares (Flying);\u00a0Running Attack","melee":"Bite (2) +12 (1d8+7); Claws (2) +12 (1d6+7); Sting +12 (2-Square\u00a0Reach) (1d6+7) plus Poison","fightingSpace":"2x2 Squares","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":6,"grapple":14,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":17,"dexterity":24,"constitution":16,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":10,"charisma":13},"feats":["4d6a68d553fb0449","a9f6de36f24ef202","252b67d6e31c377e"],"skills":["Initiative\u00a0+15 (may reroll, must take second result),\u00a0Perception\u00a0+9"],"abilityText":"Dual Mind:\u00a0Whenever an effect targets the Battle Hydra's\u00a0Will Defense, the originator of the effect must roll twice, taking the lower result.\nPoison:\u00a0If the Battle Hydra's Sting deals damage to a living target, make a follow-up attack roll (1d20+9) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense. On a hit, the target takes 3d6 points of damage and moves -1 step along the\u00a0Condition Track. The Poison attacks each round at the start of the Battle Hydra's turn until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check."}}},"items":[]}
