 opponent, it can automatically make a\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check at its full bonus as a\u00a0Free Action. If the\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check is successful, the Canyon Krayt Dragon can begin Devouring it's target.\nThe creature being Devoured takes 1d8+22 points of damage each round at the start of its turn, before it takes any actions. When the creature reaches 0 Hit Points, it is swallowed by the Canyon Krayt Dragon and continues to take 1d6 points of\u00a0Acid\u00a0damage each round at the start of its turn.\nThe Canyon Krayt Dragon cannot make Bite attacks until it releases the creature (A\u00a0Free Action) or swallows it.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Canyon Krayt Dragon","cl":14,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":6,"senses":"Low-Light Vision, Tremorsense,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+19","perception":19,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFootedDefense":15,"fortitudeDefense":26,"willDefense":13,"hitPoints":292,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"10 Squares;\u00a0Powerful Charge","melee":"Bite +24* (4d6+28); Bite +28* (4d6+35) with\u00a0Powerful Charge; Claws (2) +24* (3d6+28)","fightingSpace":"6x6 Squares","reach":"4 Squares","baseAttackBonus":11,"grapple":48,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":44,"dexterity":8,"constitution":40,"intelligence":1,"wisdom":14,"charisma":6},"feats":["f8e2a30390d870e7","3f76464c43c73f84","e73873cdc77a6451","1592aaedf4b6e40a","a9f6de36f24ef202","3d4a4e93ced26712"],"skills":["Climb\u00a0+29,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+19"],"abilityText":"Tremorsense:\u00a0A Canyon Krayt Dragon automatically senses the location of anything that is in contact with the ground and within 100 squares (No\u00a0Perception\u00a0check required).\nDevour:\u00a0If a\u00a0Canyon Krayt Dragon hits with it's Bite attack against a Huge or smaller opponent, it can automatically make a\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check at its full bonus as a\u00a0Free Action. If the\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check is successful, the Canyon Krayt Dragon can begin Devouring it's target.\nThe creature being Devoured takes 1d8+22 points of damage each round at the start of its turn, before it takes any actions. When the creature reaches 0 Hit Points, it is swallowed by the Canyon Krayt Dragon and continues to take 1d6 points of\u00a0Acid\u00a0damage each round at the start of its turn.\nThe Canyon Krayt Dragon cannot make Bite attacks until it releases the creature (A\u00a0Free Action) or swallows it."}}},"items":[]}
