ained\u00a0in\u00a0Ride, the Bolotaur always catches the rider it if catches itself while falling.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Bolotaur","cl":5,"tags":["mount","beast"],"size":"large","initiative":5,"senses":"Low-Light Vision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+4","perception":4,"reflexDefense":17,"flatFootedDefense":15,"fortitudeDefense":16,"willDefense":11,"hitPoints":63,"damageThreshold":21,"speed":"8 Squares;\u00a0Bantha Rush","melee":"Bite +10 (1d8+9); Claws (2) +10 (1d6+9)","fightingSpace":"2x2 Squares","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":4,"grapple":15,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":22,"dexterity":14,"constitution":22,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":12,"charisma":10},"feats":["fc1e5f0a2367debb","1592aaedf4b6e40a","a9f6de36f24ef202"],"skills":["Climb\u00a0+19,\u00a0Endurance\u00a0+14"],"abilityText":"Climbing Mount:\u00a0When a Bolotaur falls, it can make a\u00a0Climb\u00a0check to catch itself while falling without any increase to the\u00a0Climb\u00a0DC. (Normally, catching yourself while falling adds +20 to the DC of the surface being climbed.) If the Bolotaur is mounted by a rider\u00a0Trained\u00a0in\u00a0Ride, the Bolotaur always catches the rider it if catches itself while falling."}}},"items":[]}
