he creature being Devoured takes 4d6+30 points of damage each round at the start of its turn, before it takes any actions. When the creature reaches 0 Hit Points, it is swallowed by the Sith Wyrm and continues to take 3d6 points of\u00a0Acid\u00a0damage each round at the start of its turn.\nThe Sith Wyrm cannot make Bite attacks until it releases the creature (A\u00a0Free Action) or swallows it.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Sith Wyrm","cl":15,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":8,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+12","perception":12,"reflexDefense":26,"flatFootedDefense":26,"fortitudeDefense":40,"willDefense":25,"hitPoints":296,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"10 Squares;\u00a0Powerful Charge","melee":"Bite +27* (4d6+38); Bite +29* (4d6+46) with\u00a0Powerful Charge","fightingSpace":"6x6 Squares","reach":"4 Squares","baseAttackBonus":12,"grapple":54,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":44,"dexterity":10,"constitution":38,"intelligence":1,"wisdom":8,"charisma":10},"feats":["7bc21d4a74b95be5","96666de28ba99b64","c238f3f722689a3a","3f76464c43c73f84","e73873cdc77a6451","c41814601364b643"],"skills":["Perception\u00a0+12 (may reroll, must take second result)"],"abilityText":"Devour:\u00a0If a\u00a0Sith Wyrm hits with it's Bite attack against a Gargantuan or smaller opponent, it can automatically make a\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check at its full bonus as a\u00a0Free Action. If the\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check is successful, the Sith Wyrm can begin Devouring it's target.\nThe creature being Devoured takes 4d6+30 points of damage each round at the start of its turn, before it takes any actions. When the creature reaches 0 Hit Points, it is swallowed by the Sith Wyrm and continues to take 3d6 points of\u00a0Acid\u00a0damage each round at the start of its turn.\nThe Sith Wyrm cannot make Bite attacks until it releases the creature (A\u00a0Free Action) or swallows it."}}},"items":[]}
