ck, at makes a free attack against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense. On a success, the Droch Swarm Burrows into the target's flesh, infecting the target with the\u00a0Death Seed Plague. A Burrowed Droch Swarm can be removed with a successful DC 25\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Droch Swarm","cl":2,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":5,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0-1","perception":-1,"reflexDefense":15,"flatFootedDefense":10,"fortitudeDefense":11,"willDefense":10,"hitPoints":8,"damageThreshold":21,"speed":"6 Squares","melee":"Bite +1 (1d4,\u00a0Area Attack) with Burrow","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":0,"grapple":-14,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":2,"dexterity":20,"constitution":10,"intelligence":1,"wisdom":9,"charisma":2},"feats":["1592aaedf4b6e40a","252b67d6e31c377e"],"skills":["Stealth\u00a0+15"],"abilityText":"Light Susceptibility:\u00a0When exposed to light, a Droch Swarm moves -2\u00a0Persistent\u00a0steps down the\u00a0Condition Track. This\u00a0Persistent Condition\u00a0is removed the moment the Droch Swarm is no longer exposed to the light.\nBurrow:\u00a0When a Droch Swarm hits with its Bite attack, at makes a free attack against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense. On a success, the Droch Swarm Burrows into the target's flesh, infecting the target with the\u00a0Death Seed Plague. A Burrowed Droch Swarm can be removed with a successful DC 25\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check."}}},"items":[]}
