e Mastif Phalone can\u00a0Take 20\u00a0on\u00a0Stealth\u00a0checks to remain hidden from that target without increasing the time taken to make the\u00a0Stealth\u00a0check.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Mastif Phalone","cl":6,"tags":["beast"],"size":"large","initiative":5,"senses":"Low-Light Vision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+5","perception":5,"reflexDefense":18,"flatFootedDefense":16,"fortitudeDefense":15,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":67,"damageThreshold":20,"speed":"8 Squares;\u00a0Powerful Charge","melee":"Bite +10 (1d8+8); Claws (2) +10 (1d6+8)","fightingSpace":"2x2 Squares","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":5,"grapple":15,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":21,"dexterity":14,"constitution":20,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":15,"charisma":10},"feats":["e73873cdc77a6451","1592aaedf4b6e40a","a8511e47656ef4dd"],"skills":["Stealth\u00a0+10 (May\u00a0Take 20\u00a0against unaware targets without penalty)"],"abilityText":"Savage Frenzy:\u00a0If the Mastif Phalone has less than half of its Hit Points, it gains a +2 bonus on all attack rolls and deals +1 die of damage on all attacks.\nSavannah Hunter:\u00a0If the Mastif Phalone has\u00a0Concealment\u00a0from a target that is unaware of the Mastif Phalone, the Mastif Phalone can\u00a0Take 20\u00a0on\u00a0Stealth\u00a0checks to remain hidden from that target without increasing the time taken to make the\u00a0Stealth\u00a0check.","beastLevel":7}}},"items":[]}
