f it has already taken a\u00a0Full-Round Action). If the\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check is successful, the Sarlacc can make an opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check each round to move the\u00a0Grappled\u00a0creature 1 square closer, until it pulls the creature into its maw.\nTremorsense:\u00a0A Sarlacc automatically senses the location of anything that is in contact with the ground and within 100 squares (No\u00a0Perception\u00a0check required).","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Sarlacc","cl":12,"tags":["beast"],"size":"colossal","initiative":6,"senses":"Tremorsense,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+10","perception":10,"reflexDefense":7,"flatFootedDefense":7,"fortitudeDefense":28,"willDefense":10,"hitPoints":286,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"Immobile","melee":"Bite +25 (4d6+22); Tentacle Grab (9) +25 (See Below)","fightingSpace":"6x6 Squares","reach":"4 Squares","baseAttackBonus":9,"grapple":45,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":42,"dexterity":10,"constitution":44,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":8,"charisma":7},"feats":["96666de28ba99b64","f8e2a30390d870e7","c238f3f722689a3a","a9f6de36f24ef202","11db29efd899c438"],"skills":["Perception\u00a0+10,\u00a0Stealth\u00a0+11"],"abilityText":"Camouflage:\u00a0A Sarlacc ignores its size modifier when it makes\u00a0Stealth\u00a0checks.\nTentacle Grab:\u00a0If a Sarlacc hits with one of its tentacles against a Huge or smaller opponent, it can automatically make a\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check with its tentacle attack at its full bonus (Even if it has already taken a\u00a0Full-Round Action). If the\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check is successful, the Sarlacc can make an opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check each round to move the\u00a0Grappled\u00a0creature 1 square closer, until it pulls the creature into its maw.\nTremorsense:\u00a0A Sarlacc automatically senses the location of anything that is in contact with the ground and within 100 squares (No\u00a0Perception\u00a0check required).","beastLevel":13}}},"items":[]}
