s a -5 penalty to\u00a0Endurance\u00a0checks made to\u00a0Ignore Hunger.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Ukian Torbull","cl":0,"tags":["mount","beast"],"size":"huge","initiative":-1,"senses":"Perception\u00a0-1","perception":-1,"reflexDefense":11,"flatFootedDefense":11,"fortitudeDefense":17,"willDefense":10,"hitPoints":10,"damageThreshold":27,"speed":"12 Squares","melee":"Gore +4 (2d6+4); Tail Slam +4 (1d8+4)","fightingSpace":"3x3 Squares","reach":"2 Squares","baseAttackBonus":0,"grapple":14,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":19,"dexterity":9,"constitution":22,"intelligence":1,"wisdom":8,"charisma":3},"feats":["f8e2a30390d870e7"],"skills":["Survival\u00a0+4"],"abilityText":"Tame:\u00a0A Ukian Torbull is exceptionally docile, providing its rider a +5 favorable circumstance bonus to\u00a0Ride\u00a0checks.\nThick Hide:\u00a0Ukian Torbulls have exceptionally tough hides, providing a +3 Natural Armor bonus to\u00a0Reflex Defense.\nVoracious:\u00a0A Ukian Torbull takes a -5 penalty to\u00a0Endurance\u00a0checks made to\u00a0Ignore Hunger."}}},"items":[]}
