Rage lasts for a number of rounds equal to 5 + the mother's\u00a0Constitution\u00a0modifier. After raging, the mother moves -1\u00a0Persistent\u00a0step along the\u00a0Condition Track, and the\u00a0Persistent Condition\u00a0can be removed only if the Katarn rests for 10 minutes.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Katarn","cl":7,"tags":["beast"],"size":"medium","initiative":8,"senses":"Low-Light Vision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+6","perception":6,"reflexDefense":19,"flatFootedDefense":15,"fortitudeDefense":12,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":60,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"10 Squares","melee":"Bite +11 (1d4+9); Claws (2) +11 (1d10+9); Horns +11 (2d4+9)","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":6,"grapple":11,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":20,"dexterity":18,"constitution":15,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":15,"charisma":9},"feats":["3f76464c43c73f84","1592aaedf4b6e40a","a9f6de36f24ef202"],"skills":["Climb\u00a0+19,\u00a0Survival\u00a0+11"],"abilityText":"Maternal Rage:\u00a0If her pups are threatened, a female Katarn enters a Maternal Rage. This rage grants the mother a +2 bonus to melee attack rolls and damage rolls and a +2 bonus to\u00a0Fortitude\u00a0and\u00a0Will Defense, but it also causes a -2 penalty to her\u00a0Reflex Defense. A Maternal Rage lasts for a number of rounds equal to 5 + the mother's\u00a0Constitution\u00a0modifier. After raging, the mother moves -1\u00a0Persistent\u00a0step along the\u00a0Condition Track, and the\u00a0Persistent Condition\u00a0can be removed only if the Katarn rests for 10 minutes.","beastLevel":8}}},"items":[]}
{"_id":"ca8abefb66553f8c","name":"Taozin","type":"npc","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"isDroid":false,"droidDegree":"","attributes":{"str":{"base":30,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"dex":{"base":7,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"con":{"base":28,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"int":{"base":2,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"wis":{"base":8,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"cha":{"base":2,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0}},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"climb":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"deception":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"endurance":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"con","favorite":false},"gatherInformation":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"initiative":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"jump":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"knowledgeBureaucracy":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeGalacticLore":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeLifeSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgePhysicalSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeSocialSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTactics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTechnology":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"mechanics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"perception":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"persuasion":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"pilot":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"ride":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"stealth":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"survival":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"swim":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"treatInjury":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"wis","favorite":false},"useComputer":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"useTheForce":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false}},"hp":{"value":175,"max":175,"temp":0,"bonus":0},"conditionTrack":{"current":0,"persistent":false,"penalty":0},"level":12,"size":"gargantuan","speed":4,"defenses":{"reflex":{"total":18,"armor":0,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"dex","source":"level","level":0},"fort":{"total":32,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"con","level":0},"will":{"total":22,"classBonus":0,"misc":{"auto":{},"user":{}},"ability":"wis","level":0},"flatFooted":{"total":18}},"languages":[],"destinyPoints":{"value":0,"max":0},"forcePoints":{"value":0,"max":0,"die":"1d6"},"darkSideScore":0,"damageThreshold":0,"bab":9,"race":"","class":"","className":"","biography":"Invisible to the Force:\u00a0A Taozin cannot be detected using any\u00a0Force Power,\u00a0Force Talent, or the\u00a0Use the Force\u00a0skill. This includes all Talents on the\u00a0Sense Talent Tree\u00a0as well as the\u00a0Sense Force,\u00a0Sense Surroundings, and\u00a0Telepathy\u00a0applications of the\u00a0Use the Force\u00a0skill.\nLightsaber Diffusion:\u00a0When a Taozin is hit by a\u00a0Lightsaber, it makes an attack roll (1d20+10) against the attacker as a\u00a0Reaction. If the attack hits, the target takes 2d8 points of Energy damage.\nTranslucent:\u00a0A Taozin ignores its size modifier when it makes\u00a0Stealth\u00a0checks. In addition, the Taozin is always considered to have\u00a0Concealment\u00a0in normal lighting conditions and\u00a0Total Concealment\u00a0in low-light conditions against creatures more than 6 squares away.\nWeb:\u00a0As a\u00a0Standard Action, a Taozin can spew an adhesive substance from its mouth and make an\u00a0Area Attack\u00a0against the\u00a0Reflex Defense: of every creature in a 4x4 square area, no square of which can be farther than 20 squares from the Taozin. Targets hit by this attack are\u00a0Immobilized\u00a0until they escape.\nA character can escape by making a DC 20\u00a0Strength\u00a0or\u00a0Acrobatics\u00a0checks check as a\u00a0Standard Action. If any square with webbing in it takes Energy or\u00a0Fire\u00a0damage, the webs in that square are destroyed and any creature\u00a0Immobilized\u00a0by the webs in that space takes 1d6 points of damage and is no longer\u00a0Immobilized.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Taozin","cl":12,"tags":["beast"],"size":"gargantuan","initiative":4,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+5","perception":5,"reflexDefense":18,"flatFootedDefense":18,"fortitudeDefense":32,"willDefense":22,"hitPoints":175,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"4 Squares","melee":"Bite +14* (3d6+21)","fightingSpace":"4x4 Squares","reach":"3 Squares","baseAttackBonus":9,"grapple":34,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":30,"dexterity":7,"constitution":28,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":8,"charisma":2},"feats":["96666de28ba99b64","3f76464c43c73f84","1592aaedf4b6e40a","a9f6de36f24ef202","a9f6de36f24ef202"],"skills":["Climb\u00a0+21,\u00a0Stealth\u00a0+14,\u00a0Survival\u00a0+10"],"abilityText":"Invisible to the Force:\u00a0A Taozin cannot be detected using any\u00a0Force Power,\u00a0Force Talent, or the\u00a0Use the Force\u00a0skill. This includes all Talents on the\u00a0Sense Talent Tree\u00a0as well as the\u00a0Sense Force,\u00a0Sense Surroundings, and\u00a0Telepathy\u00a0applications of the\u00a0Use the Force\u00a0skill.\nLightsaber Diffusion:\u00a0When a Taozin is hit by a\u00a0Lightsaber, it makes an attack roll (1d20+10) against the attacker as a\u00a0Reaction. If the attack hits, the target takes 2d8 points of Energy damage.\nTranslucent:\u00a0A Taozin ignores its size modifier when it makes\u00a0Stealth\u00a0checks. In addition, the Taozin is always considered to have\u00a0Concealment\u00a0in normal lighting conditions and\u00a0Total Concealment\u00a0in low-light conditions against creatures more than 6 squares away.\nWeb:\u00a0As a\u00a0Standard Action, a Taozin can spew an adhesive substance from its mouth and make an\u00a0Area Attack\u00a0against the\u00a0Reflex Defense: of every creature in a 4x4 square area, no square of which can be farther than 20 squares from the Taozin. Targets hit by this attack are\u00a0Immobilized\u00a0until they escape.\nA character can escape by making a DC 20\u00a0Strength\u00a0or\u00a0Acrobatics\u00a0checks check as a\u00a0Standard Action. If any square with webbing in it takes Energy or\u00a0Fire\u00a0damage, the webs in that square are destroyed and any creature\u00a0Immobilized\u00a0by the webs in that space takes 1d6 points of damage and is no longer\u00a0Immobilized.","beastLevel":13}}},"items":[]}
