ad be unconscious.\nWeb Snare:\u00a0An Energy Spider can shoot a bundle of webbing up to 6 squares as a ranged\u00a0Grapple\u00a0attack. If it succeeds, the Energy Spider pulls the target into its square as a\u00a0Standard Action\u00a0by succeeding on an opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check. The target can free itself with a successful opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check (as with any other\u00a0Grapple), or it can attempt to destroy the webbing. The webbing has 5 Hit Points, DR 15/Slashing, and has a break DC of 25.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Energy Spider","cl":5,"tags":["beast"],"size":null,"initiative":12,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+4","perception":4,"reflexDefense":19,"flatFootedDefense":15,"fortitudeDefense":12,"willDefense":11,"hitPoints":39,"damageThreshold":null,"speed":"6 Squares\u00a0(Walking), 6 Squares (Climbing)","melee":"Sting +6 (1d4+2) with Life Drain","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"2 Squares","baseAttackBonus":4,"grapple":8,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":15,"dexterity":18,"constitution":14,"intelligence":3,"wisdom":13,"charisma":7},"feats":["c238f3f722689a3a","a9f6de36f24ef202","a8511e47656ef4dd"],"skills":["Initiative\u00a0+12,\u00a0Stealth\u00a0+12"],"abilityText":"Life Drain:\u00a0Any living creature damaged by the Energy Spider's Sting attack also moves -1\u00a0Persistent\u00a0step on the\u00a0Condition Track. A living creature reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack is killed automatically, but that creature may spend a\u00a0Force Point\u00a0to instead be unconscious.\nWeb Snare:\u00a0An Energy Spider can shoot a bundle of webbing up to 6 squares as a ranged\u00a0Grapple\u00a0attack. If it succeeds, the Energy Spider pulls the target into its square as a\u00a0Standard Action\u00a0by succeeding on an opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check. The target can free itself with a successful opposed\u00a0Grapple\u00a0check (as with any other\u00a0Grapple), or it can attempt to destroy the webbing. The webbing has 5 Hit Points, DR 15/Slashing, and has a break DC of 25."}}},"items":[]}
