s bonus to\u00a0Jump\u00a0checks to determine the distance cleared.\nin:\u00a0Nonheroic Units,\u00a0Beasts\nReyko\nEdit\nReference Book:\u00a0Star Wars Saga Edition Unknown Regions\nAffiliations:\u00a0Beasts\nThe most common beast on\u00a0Volik\u00a0is the Reyko, a docile herd animal similar to the\u00a0Bantha. Reykos are covered with hard, chitinous skin that, to the untrained eye, makes the creatures look like the many large boulders that cover the\u00a0Volik\u00a0landscape. They feed on the plentiful grass of the plains and use their camouflage to hide from predators. The smuggler havens that crop up on\u00a0Volik\u00a0often harness Reykos as beasts of burden. The animals are slow but powerful, and a team of them can haul a wrecked starfighter back to base for salvage. Reykos can also withstand blaster fire, so smugglers sometimes use them to ram\u00a0Wind Skiffs\u00a0and\u00a0Speeders\u00a0piloted by rivals.\nContents","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Strill","cl":4,"tags":["beast"],"size":"small","initiative":4,"senses":"Perception\u00a0+13","perception":13,"reflexDefense":14,"flatFootedDefense":12,"fortitudeDefense":13,"willDefense":12,"hitPoints":39,"damageThreshold":13,"speed":"4 Squares; Glide","melee":"Bite +9 (1d4+8)","fightingSpace":"1 Square","reach":"1 Square","baseAttackBonus":3,"grapple":4,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":22,"dexterity":14,"constitution":14,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":12,"charisma":3},"feats":["f8e2a30390d870e7","1592aaedf4b6e40a"],"skills":["Perception\u00a0+13"],"abilityText":"Carrying Capacity:\u00a0Strills are treated as Medium creatures when determining their\u00a0Carrying Capacity.\nGlide:\u00a0As a\u00a0Move Action, a Strill can glide, which is treated as a\u00a0Jump\u00a0check (+8) with the Strill being considered to have a running start. Strills gain a +10 Species bonus to\u00a0Jump\u00a0checks to determine the distance cleared.\nin:\u00a0Nonheroic Units,\u00a0Beasts\nReyko\nEdit\nReference Book:\u00a0Star Wars Saga Edition Unknown Regions\nAffiliations:\u00a0Beasts\nThe most common beast on\u00a0Volik\u00a0is the Reyko, a docile herd animal similar to the\u00a0Bantha. Reykos are covered with hard, chitinous skin that, to the untrained eye, makes the creatures look like the many large boulders that cover the\u00a0Volik\u00a0landscape. They feed on the plentiful grass of the plains and use their camouflage to hide from predators. The smuggler havens that crop up on\u00a0Volik\u00a0often harness Reykos as beasts of burden. The animals are slow but powerful, and a team of them can haul a wrecked starfighter back to base for salvage. Reykos can also withstand blaster fire, so smugglers sometimes use them to ram\u00a0Wind Skiffs\u00a0and\u00a0Speeders\u00a0piloted by rivals.\nContents","beastLevel":5}}},"items":[]}
{"_id":"fa2b51a9a3ace744","name":"Knobby White Spider","type":"npc","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","system":{"isDroid":false,"droidDegree":"","attributes":{"str":{"base":26,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"dex":{"base":14,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"con":{"base":34,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"int":{"base":2,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"wis":{"base":12,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0},"cha":{"base":10,"racial":0,"enhancement":0,"temp":0}},"skills":{"acrobatics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"climb":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"deception":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"endurance":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"con","favorite":false},"gatherInformation":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"cha","favorite":false},"initiative":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"dex","favorite":false},"jump":{"trained":true,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"str","favorite":false},"knowledgeBureaucracy":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeGalacticLore":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeLifeSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgePhysicalSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeSocialSciences":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTactics":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"knowledgeTechnology":{"trained":false,"focused":false,"miscMod":0,"selectedAbility":"int","favorite":false},"mechanics":{"trained":false,"focused":f