the end of the\u00a0Condition Track\u00a0by the Poison is\u00a0Immobilized, but not unconscious. The Poison attacks each round until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.","derived":{}},"effects":[],"flags":{"swse":{"beastData":{"name":"Knobby White Spider","cl":8,"tags":["beast"],"size":"huge","initiative":6,"senses":"Darkvision,\u00a0Perception\u00a0+5","perception":5,"reflexDefense":16,"flatFootedDefense":14,"fortitudeDefense":22,"willDefense":11,"hitPoints":130,"damageThreshold":37,"speed":"6 Squares","melee":"Bite +14 (2d6+12); Bite +12 (3d6+12) with\u00a0Rapid Strike; Sting +14 (1d8+12) plus Poison; Sting +12 (2d8+12) plus Poison with\u00a0Rapid Strike","fightingSpace":"3x3 Squares","reach":"2 Squares","baseAttackBonus":6,"grapple":24,"speciesTraits":[],"abilities":{"strength":26,"dexterity":14,"constitution":34,"intelligence":2,"wisdom":12,"charisma":10},"feats":["96666de28ba99b64","ccb33e58342499a3","a9f6de36f24ef202","11db29efd899c438"],"skills":["Endurance\u00a0+21,\u00a0Jump\u00a0+17"],"abilityText":"Poison:\u00a0If the Sting of a Knobby White Spider deals damage to a living target, the target is also poisoned. If the Poison succeeds on an attack roll (1d20+10) against the target's\u00a0Fortitude Defense, the target moves -1 step along the\u00a0Condition Track. A target moved to the end of the\u00a0Condition Track\u00a0by the Poison is\u00a0Immobilized, but not unconscious. The Poison attacks each round until cured with a successful DC 15\u00a0Treat Injury\u00a0check.","beastLevel":9}}},"items":[]}
